{"tid":2085202,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【煽動顛覆國家政權罪】例子","createTime":"2020-06-29T17:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T18:11:58.000Z","uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c56bbdac22cb3a744d636c46b90990bd157ccb","tid":2085202,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"呢條友叫 權平<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/ql1-02152017120309.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Frenquanfazhi%2Fql1-02152017120309.html&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=2ba2979e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/ql1-02152017120309.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S50CWYV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS50CWYV.png&h=24ecd50b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n相片疑攝於2016年9月1日<br />\n拍左一張相 up上網 咁就犯左【煽動顛覆國家政權罪】了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/權平\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%AC%8A%E5%B9%B3&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=97ee8e5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/權平</a><br />\n2016年10月1日 失蹤<br />\nwiki話2017年2月15日上午9點30分在延邊朝鮮族自治州中級法院開庭，現被關押在延邊市看守所。而家好似仲未判 未有消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件進展<br />\n<br />\n2016年9月1日，權平穿上一件印有「XITLER」「習包子」和「大撒幣」的白色T恤上班，以「習特勒」（Xitler）諷刺習近平是希特勒，並將其自拍上傳至個人Twitter。同月30日，權平向海外朋友透露，打算在10月1日穿批習標語的衣服上街[2]，結果當晚其美國朋友、留美學生古懿收到他發出緊急訊息表示「出事了」，之後便沒有與他有關的信息。外界在多月後才確認，權平被秘密拘捕[3]。<br />\n<br />\n全美中國學生學者自治聯合會（簡稱為全美學自聯）於2016年11月1日發表聲明，敦促中國政府立即無條件釋放權平。[4]11月13日，20多名華裔人士，到中國駐舊金山總領事館門外抗議，要求立即釋放權平[5]。<br />\n<br />\n2017年2月15日上午9點30分該案在延邊朝鮮族自治州中級法院開庭。<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">權平以前的兩名辯護律師在此案即將審理的幾天前突然被解聘。</span></strong>梁小軍是被解聘的律師之一。[6]<br />\n<br />\n2018年底，中國政府加強對Twitter的審查。[7] <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nwiki仲有好多其他案例睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/煽動顛覆國家政權罪\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E9%A1%9B%E8%A6%86%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A%E7%BD%AA&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=93e76660\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/煽動顛覆國家政權罪</a>"},{"pid":"fb361c85699038c13c6264048c60c07e6c822e9d","tid":2085202,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:58:36.000Z","msg":"大家得閒都可以幫手寫下維基百科<br />\n有興趣了解維基百科嘅可以入嚟睇下教學<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2074204/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2074204/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7854b851718d7c83110f5c6621d3a9c67fdbbc9e","tid":2085202,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:58:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b646bdcab7c75cd02bafe95b049d132d036f630","tid":2085202,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:01:58.000Z","msg":"例子真係多到無限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f71a29ad99f4f903d501ca4fe9cac3be0703c7","tid":2085202,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdAzeQd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdAzeQd.gif&h=b397ea02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERfrQoJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FERfrQoJ.gif&h=9cd071ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41cfe70e5484131af9dffe9af1227b5f1ee6a26b","tid":2085202,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27f71a29ad99f4f903d501ca4fe9cac3be0703c7","tid":2085202,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdAzeQd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdAzeQd.gif&h=b397ea02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERfrQoJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FERfrQoJ.gif&h=9cd071ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1706d964f0bf11363ab224304bf40cc45f2cb5","tid":2085202,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T18:11:58.000Z","msg":"709個班全部唔係顛覆國家政權,就係煽動顛覆國家政權"}]}